## 6. `ctx.ui.custom()` → `showOverlay` mapping

From `dist/modes/interactive/interactive-mode.js` line 1880:
```js
const handle = this.ui.showOverlay(component, resolveOptions());
```

Confirmed via `docs/tui.md`: when `{ overlay: true }` is passed, `ctx.ui.custom()` calls `tui.showOverlay(component, overlayOptions)` internally. The `overlayOptions` object is passed straight through to `showOverlay`'s options parameter.

